penderitaanmu.

67
00:05:44,822 --> 00:05:46,456
Menurutmu apa yang akan

68
00:05:47,449 --> 00:05:49,001
dikatakan Yeon-u?

69
00:05:49,952 --> 00:05:52,963
Apa dia akan bilang,
"Terima kasih sudah membalas"?

70
00:05:54,999 --> 00:05:56,383
Bisakah aku

71
00:05:57,418 --> 00:05:59,595
melihatnya lagi?

72
00:06:02,131 --> 00:06:03,724
Dia pasti

73
00:06:04,508 --> 00:06:06,643
ada di tempat lebih baik.

74
00:06:08,929 --> 00:06:12,190
Bagaimana aku bisa menemuinya?

75
00:06:15,561 --> 00:06:18,864
Aku melakukannya dengan penuh kesadaran
atas semua konsekuensinya.

76
00:06:20,190 --> 00:06:22,284
Aku mau mereka mengalami hal serupa.

77
00:06:23,110 --> 00:06:24,369
Bukan sekadar

78
00:06:26,238 --> 00:06:28,707
pembalasan dendam Yeon-u.

79
00:06:29,533 --> 00:06:31,335
Aku harus melakukannya

80
00:06:31,869 --> 00:06:35,547
agar bisa menjalani sisa kehidupanku
yang tak adil ini.

81
00:06:40,044 --> 00:06:41,428
Itu alasan perbuatanku.

82
00:06:42,212 --> 00:06:43,513
Jadi?

83
00:06:46,050 --> 00:06:47,935
Di mana dia sekarang?

84
00:06:50,679 --> 00:06:52,064
Jeong Sang-hun.

85
00:06:56,143 --> 00:06:58,937
Tae-sik, kurasa bukan di sini.

86
00:06:58,938 --> 00:07:01,365
Kami sudah geledah seluruh area,

87
00:07:01,941 --> 00:07:03,408
tapi dia tak ada.

88
00:07:03,817 --> 00:07:05,452
Begitu. Baiklah.

89
00:07:13,869 --> 00:07:18,465
Jika Pak Jeong sudah di luar
saat kita tiba...

90
00:07:31,679 --> 00:07:33,855
Dia berkendara pergi.

91
00:07:36,350 --> 00:07:38,652
Dia mestinya kabur lebih awal
jika ada waktu.

92
00:07:39,144 --> 00:07:40,612
Kenapa dia masih di sana?

93
00:07:50,406 --> 00:07:51,623
Kau

94
00:07:52,116 --> 00:07:53,667
membunuh Jeong Sang-hun?

95
00:07:58,288 --> 00:07:59,548
Mana jasadnya?

96
00:07:59,832 --> 00:08:01,341
Kau sembunyikan di mana?

97
00:08:02,292 --> 00:08:03,468
Aku menguburnya.

98
00:08:08,048 --> 00:08:11,518
- Aku mengubur jenazahnya.
- Benarkah?

99
00:08:16,390 --> 00:08:17,774
Di mana?

100
00:08:19,018 --> 00:08:20,235
Kau kubur di mana?

101
00:08:22,146 --> 00:08:24,573
Ada apa? Lokasinya bukan di peta ini?

102
00:08:25,858 --> 00:08:27,784
Kau menguburnya di luar negeri?

103
00:08:31,905 --> 00:08:33,915
Dia masih hidup, bukan?

104
00:08:38,370 --> 00:08:42,466
Mulai dari Cheongju, kami geledah
setiap tempat yang berkaitan denganmu,

105
00:08:42,708 --> 00:08:46,136
tapi tak ada jejak Pak Jeong,
kecuali ruang bawah tanah vila.

106
00:08:47,755 --> 00:08:50,048
Tanganmu berlumuran darah saat tertangkap,

107
00:08:50,049 --> 00:08:52,017
seolah-olah kau baru membunuhnya.

108
00:08:53,260 --> 00:08:55,261
Namun, kecuali setir mobil,

109
00:08:55,262 --> 00:08:57,472
tak ditemukan setetes darah pun
di mobilmu.

110
00:08:57,473 --> 00:08:58,774
Darah di tanganmu

111
00:08:59,391 --> 00:09:00,650
sengaja dioleskan.

112
00:09:01,393 --> 00:09:05,822
Agar kami berpikir
kau membunuh Jeong Sang-hun.

113
00:09:09,985 --> 00:09:11,328
Di mana

114
00:09:13,739 --> 00:09:15,165
Jin Yeong-min sekarang?

115
00:09:17,910 --> 00:09:22,047
Hari itu, kau sudah sejam lebih di vila

116
00:09:22,873 --> 00:09:24,383
sebelum melihat kami.

117
00:09:25,375 --> 00:09:28,387
Apa yang kau lakukan di sana
selama satu setengah jam?

118
00:09:29,296 --> 00:09:32,307
Kau sengaja menunggu kami tiba, bukan?

119
00:09:33,550 --> 00:09:35,519
Kau mengulur waktu

120
00:09:35,761 --> 00:09:38,146
agar Jin Yeong-min kabur
dengan Jeong Sang-hun.

121
00:09:44,019 --> 00:09:47,021
Hari itu, dia menuju Cheongju
setelah rapat pemegang saham.

122
00:09:47,022 --> 00:09:48,564
Kenapa hanya kau yang terlihat?

123
00:09:48,565 --> 00:09:51,493
Kalian sudah membuat rencana

124
00:09:52,653 --> 00:09:54,413
agar kami tak bisa mengejarnya.

125
00:09:57,116 --> 00:10:00,252
Dia membawa Jeong Sang-hun.

126
00:10:01,078 --> 00:10:04,297
Artinya, Jeong Sang-hun masih hidup.

127
00:10:12,172 --> 00:10:13,557
Kenapa?

128
00:10:14,716 --> 00:10:16,893
Kenapa bekerja sama dengannya?

129
00:10:17,970 --> 00:10:20,897
Aku paham alasanmu demi Yeon-u,
tapi Jin Yeong-min

130
00:10:21,515 --> 00:10:24,609
hanya ingin menyingkirkan semua orang
yang menghalanginya

131
00:10:24,935 --> 00:10:27,320
untuk menguasai JQ.

132
00:10:27,855 --> 00:10:29,781
Kenapa kau mau dipancing

133
00:10:30,524 --> 00:10:32,701
untuk melakukan kejahatan mengerikan?

134
00:10:35,028 --> 00:10:36,496
Jin Yeong-min

135
00:10:37,781 --> 00:10:39,499
hanya memanfaatkanmu.

136
00:10:41,451 --> 00:10:42,794
Dia memperalatmu.

137
00:10:45,581 --> 00:10:47,382
Tidak, kau salah.

138
00:10:54,298 --> 00:10:56,433
Penderitaan kami sama.

139
00:10:57,467 --> 00:10:58,768
Itu sebabnya

140
00:10:59,761 --> 00:11:01,605
kami merencanakan ini bersama.

141
00:11:06,184 --> 00:11:07,944
Jin Yeong-min, pria itu...

142
00:11:09,771 --> 00:11:11,156
sama sepertiku.

143
00:11:13,817 --> 00:11:18,538
Dia pun kehilangan orang
yang paling disayanginya.

144
00:11:20,782 --> 00:11:22,167
"Paling disayangi"?

145
00:11:23,327 --> 00:11:24,669
Siapa maksudmu?

146
00:11:29,666 --> 00:11:31,092
Choe Su-hyeon.

147
00:11:46,058 --> 00:11:47,817
Aku sungguh tak tahu lagi.

148
00:11:50,562 --> 00:11:53,073
Awal semua ini karenamu,

149
00:11:55,400 --> 00:11:57,244
atau aku?

150
00:12:03,700 --> 00:12:06,127
- Hei, Eun-seong!
- Yeong-min.

151
00:12:07,245 --> 00:12:08,746
Sudah lama sekali.

152
00:12:08,747 --> 00:12:10,206
- Benar, 'kan?
- Ya.

153
00:12:10,207 --> 00:12:13,134
- Apa kabar?
- Baik. Bagaimana kau?

154
00:12:13,168 --> 00:12:16,012
- Tentu baik juga.
- Yeong-min.

155
00:12:16,296 --> 00:12:17,597
- Paman Jeong.
- Hai.

156
00:12:19,466 --> 00:12:21,977
Mulai kini, panggil dia Sang-hun.

157
00:12:22,302 --> 00:12:23,687
Apa?

158
00:12:24,304 --> 00:12:25,596
Maksudmu, Eun-seong?

159
00:12:25,597 --> 00:12:29,985
Yeong-min, mulai sekarang,
kau harus menjaga Sang-hun.

160
00:12:30,477 --> 00:12:32,269
Pastikan dia tak dirundung siapa pun

161
00:12:32,270 --> 00:12:35,824
dan tak melakukan hal berbahaya.
Jaga dia baik-baik, ya?

162
00:12:39,194 --> 00:12:40,787
Bawa dia.

163
00:12:42,072 --> 00:12:43,748
Sang-hun, ayo pergi.

164
00:12:45,075 --> 00:12:46,751
Kau senang naik sepeda?

165
00:12:54,376 --> 00:12:55,969
<i>Seumur hidup,</i>

166
00:12:57,004 --> 00:12:59,556
<i>aku tak pernah dipilih oleh siapa pun.</i>

167
00:13:00,340 --> 00:13:01,850
<i>Kau tahu rasanya?</i>

168
00:13:08,890 --> 00:13:11,443
Makanan kantin tak enak.
Ayo jajan di luar.

169
00:13:11,601 --> 00:13:13,778
- Ayo.
- Hei.

170
00:13:14,521 --> 00:13:15,855
- Sang-hun.
- Hai.

171
00:13:15,856 --> 00:13:18,241
- Kudengar, kau dapat ponsel baru.
- Ya.

172
00:13:18,442 --> 00:13:21,953
Ada pemutar MP3 juga.
Ponsel lamamu berikan saja padaku.

173
00:13:22,237 --> 00:13:25,040
Jangan konyol.
Pasti diberikan ke Yeong-min.

174
00:13:26,658 --> 00:13:28,075
Untuk apa kau belajar?

175
00:13:28,076 --> 00:13:31,296
Benar. Jadi anak buah Sang-hun saja
seumur hidup.

176
00:13:32,330 --> 00:13:33,590
Baiklah.

177
00:13:33,790 --> 00:13:35,374
Aku tak mau dipanggil anak buah.

178
00:13:35,375 --> 00:13:37,543
Mulai kini, panggil aku pelayannya, paham?

179
00:13:37,544 --> 00:13:39,929
- "Pelayan"?
- Itu memang patut dibanggakan.

180
00:13:40,172 --> 00:13:42,131
- Kupikir itu bagus.
- Ayolah.

181
00:13:42,132 --> 00:13:44,059
<i>Namun, itu menjadi keseharianku,</i>

182
00:13:45,218 --> 00:13:46,644
<i>dan aku terbiasa.</i>

183
00:13:57,814 --> 00:13:59,157
Kau bosan?

184
00:13:59,941 --> 00:14:01,242
Tidak.

185
00:14:01,610 --> 00:14:03,370
Kenapa terus melihat jam?

186
00:14:04,196 --> 00:14:05,622
Hanya kebiasaan.

187
00:14:09,368 --> 00:14:10,627
Baiklah.

188
00:14:11,244 --> 00:14:12,671
- Mulai kini...
- Astaga.

189
00:14:12,829 --> 00:14:14,714
Jangan memaksakan diri.

190
00:14:17,751 --> 00:14:20,637
Jangan gelisah dan berusaha terlalu keras.

191
00:14:22,714 --> 00:14:24,849
Aku suka dirimu apa adanya.

192
00:14:25,092 --> 00:14:28,853
Santai saja dan berbahagia selamanya.

193
00:14:30,889 --> 00:14:32,399
Ya?

194
00:14:36,603 --> 00:14:37,987
<i>Pertama kali kudengar</i>

195
00:14:39,147 --> 00:14:41,116
<i>bahwa aku tak perlu berusaha keras</i>

196
00:14:42,859 --> 00:14:46,287
<i>dan bisa dicintai sebagaimana adanya.</i>

197
00:14:53,412 --> 00:14:55,255
<i>Namun, aku kehilangan dia.</i>

198
00:14:58,083 --> 00:15:00,218
<i>Bahkan tak sempat berterima kasih.</i>

199
00:15:01,128 --> 00:15:02,303
<i>Itu karenamu,</i>

200
00:15:04,256 --> 00:15:05,807
<i>dan aku.</i>

201
00:15:13,598 --> 00:15:17,360
Pak Choi akan membeli tanah
untuk kompleks bisnis itu.

202
00:15:17,727 --> 00:15:19,779
<i>- Juga karena mereka.</i>
- Begitu.

203
00:15:20,939 --> 00:15:22,323
Harganya?

204
00:15:31,825 --> 00:15:33,951
Kenapa Sang-hun? Kenapa harus dia?

205
00:15:33,952 --> 00:15:35,754
- Bu Kim.
- Teganya...

206
00:15:35,954 --> 00:15:38,164
Kenapa kau memperalat Sang-hun
untuk balas dendam?

207
00:15:38,165 --> 00:15:41,625
- Tenanglah.
- Dia berusaha menolongmu!

208
00:15:41,626 --> 00:15:42,927
Dia tak buat apa pun.

209
00:15:46,506 --> 00:15:47,849
Pada akhirnya,

210
00:15:49,092 --> 00:15:50,935
dia tak berbuat apa pun.

211
00:15:56,433 --> 00:15:58,067
Bisakah kau berbuat sesuatu?

212
00:16:05,317 --> 00:16:07,526
Apa maksudmu? Apa artinya itu?

213
00:16:07,527 --> 00:16:08,986
- Cukup.
- Apa artinya?

214
00:16:08,987 --> 00:16:11,206
- Hentikan.
- Apa maksudmu?

215
00:16:23,710 --> 00:16:25,845
Astaga, Pak.

216
00:16:26,171 --> 00:16:27,514
Pak! Kumohon...

217
00:16:30,550 --> 00:16:33,812
Aku memang tak berguna,

218
00:16:34,012 --> 00:16:37,440
masa bodoh dengan yang terjadi padaku,

219
00:16:37,724 --> 00:16:38,983
tapi Dong-gu...

220
00:16:39,601 --> 00:16:40,944
Dong-gu...

221
00:16:41,269 --> 00:16:43,947
Jangan dia, Pak.

222
00:16:46,149 --> 00:16:48,993
Tolonglah, kumohon padamu.

223
00:16:50,737 --> 00:16:54,624
Tolong dia sekali ini saja.

224
00:16:54,950 --> 00:16:58,336
Tolong bantu putraku, Dong-gu.

225
00:16:58,995 --> 00:17:01,047
Sekali ini saja, kumohon.

226
00:17:02,290 --> 00:17:06,052
Tolong selamatkan dia, Pak.

227
00:17:06,962 --> 00:17:09,347
Pak...

228
00:17:09,673 --> 00:17:12,267
Pak Son, dengarkan.

229
00:17:14,511 --> 00:17:19,357
Membesarkan anak bukan tugas mudah, bukan?

230
00:17:20,392 --> 00:17:22,193
Aku sudah tua,

231
00:17:22,811 --> 00:17:27,782
jadi, merasa bisa berbuat seenaknya
dalam banyak hal.

232
00:17:28,984 --> 00:17:30,493
Namun, anehnya,

233
00:17:31,278 --> 00:17:33,955
aku tak bisa bersikap begitu pada putraku.

234
00:17:35,782 --> 00:17:37,917
Apa boleh buat?

235
00:17:39,202 --> 00:17:43,923
Hanya orang tua yang menyayangi anak
